spec_data.Name: perl-LWP-Protocol-PSGI
spec_data.Description:
LWP::Protocol::PSGI is a module to hijack any code that uses LWP::UserAgent
underneath such that any HTTP or HTTPS requests can be routed to your own
PSGI application.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Fri 28 Jul 2017 12:47:33 PM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Override LWP's HTTP/HTTPS backend with your own PSGI application
